Package bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.test

package bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.test
Contains unit tests and test utilities for the flight booking system.

This package includes JUnit test cases for validating system functionality and components. Tests cover model classes, authentication, validation utilities, and business logic.

Test Classes:

  • FlightTest - Flight model tests
  • CustomerTest - Customer model tests
  • BookingTest - Booking model tests
  • AuthenticationServiceTest - Auth tests
  • ValidationUtilTest - Validation tests
